column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, s.specobjid, p.type, s.class, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r,  p.expRad_r, p.expRadErr_r, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.Err, g.bptclass, p.lgm_tot_p5#, p.sfr_tot_p5#, p.specsfr_tot_p5# FROM photoobj as p JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN galSpecExtra as g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE type = #
